Invocation Name: washington tweets
des:
Listen to the most recent tweets from twenty of the most familiar and recognizable names in Washington DC politics.

This includes President Trump, Nancy Pelosi, Mike Pence, Paul Ryan, Bernie Sanders, Hillary Clinton, Chuck Schumer, and others.

The tweets are linked through IFTTT, Twitter, and Google Sheets and appear here as soon as they are posted.

The tweets are time and date stamped so you know when they were posted.

The tweets appear on the screen of Echo Show along with a photo of the person who made the tweet.

The tweets are spoken as they were written. However url links are excluded. @ symbols and # tags are spoken but do not link.
